<html><head><style>body{font-family:'Segoe UI', Calibri, sans-serif; line-height:1.6;} h1{color:#2E4053; border-bottom:2px solid #2E4053;} h2{color:#2874A6;} code{background:#F4F6F6; padding:2px; font-family:Consolas, monospace;}</style></head><body><h1>HTML Template: attendance_history.html</h1>
<h2>1. Executive Summary</h2>
<p>Defines the structural layout and content for a specific web page view.</p>
<h2>2. Code Logic &amp; Functionality</h2>
<p>Uses the Jinja2 templating engine. The file allows for dynamic data insertion using <code>{{ variable }}</code> syntax and control structures like <code>{% if %}</code> loops within standard HTML markup.</p>
<h2>3. Key Concepts &amp; Definitions</h2>
<ul>
<li><strong>Jinja2</strong>: A modern and designer-friendly templating language for Python.</li>
<li><strong>Template Inheritance</strong>: The ability to extend a base layout (<code>base.html</code>) to avoid code duplication.</li>
<li><strong>DOM</strong>: Document Object Model, the data representation of the objects that comprise the structure and content of a document on the web.</li>
</ul>
<h2>4. Location Details</h2>
<p><strong>Path</strong>: <code>templates\tutor\attendance_history.html</code>
<strong>Type</strong>: .HTML File</p>
<h2>5. Source Code Preview (Snippet)</h2>
<p>Running typical software analysis on this file:</p>
<p>```html
{% extends "base.html" %}</p>
<p>{% block title %}Attendance History - {{ activity.name }}{% endblock %}</p>
<p>{% block content %}</p>
<div class="container py-5">
    <div class="row justify-content-center">
        <div class="col-lg-11">
            <div class="mb-4">
                <a href="{{ url_for('tutor_dashboard') }}" class="text-decoration-none text-muted mb-2 d-inline-block">
                    <i class="fas fa-arrow-left me-1"></i> Back to Dashboard
                </a>
                <h2 class="text-primary mb-0">Attendance History: {{ activity.name }}</h2>
                <p class="text-muted">{{ activity.day_of_week }} | {{ activity.start_time }} - {{ activity.end_time }}
                </p>
            </div>

            {% if attendance_records %}
            <div class="card shadow-sm">
                <div class="card-header bg-primary text-white p-4">
                    <h5 class="mb-0"><i class="fas fa-history me-2"></i>All Attendance Sessions</h5>
                </div>
                <div class="card-body p-4">
                    {% for record in attendance_records %}
                    <div class="mb-4 border-bottom pb-4">
                        <div class="d-flex justify-content-between align-items-center mb-3">
                            <h5 class="text-primary mb-0">
                                <i class="fas fa-calendar me-2"></i>{{ record.date.strftime('%A, %B %d, %Y') }}
                            </h5>
                            <div>
                                <span class="badge bg-success me-2">
                                    <i class="fas fa-check"></i> {{ record.present or 0 }} Present
                                </span>
                                <span class="badge bg-warning me-2">
                                    <i class="fas fa-clock"></i> {{ record.late or 0 }} Late
                                </span>
                                <span class="badge bg-danger">
                                    <i class="fas fa-times"></i> {{ record.absent or 0 }} Absent
                                </span>
                            </div>
                        </div>

                        <div class="table-responsive">
                            <table class="table table-sm table-hover mb-0">
                                <thead class="table-light">
                                    <tr>
                                        <th>Student</th>
                                        <th>Grade</th>
                                        <th>Status</th>
                                    </tr>
                                </thead>
                                <tbody>
                                    {% for attendance in detailed_records[record.date] %}
                                    <tr>
                                        <td>
                                            <div class="d-flex align-items-center">
                                                <div class="avatar-sm bg-light text-primary me-2">
                                                    {{ attendance.child.name[0] }}
                                                </div>
                                                {{ attendance.child.name }}
                                            </div>
                                        </td>
                                        <td>Grade {{ attendance.child.grade }}</td>
                                        <td>
                                            {% if attendance.status == 'present' %}
                                            <span class="badge bg-success">
                                                <i class="fas fa-check"></i> Present
                                            </span>
                                            {% elif attendance.status == 'late' %}
                                            <span class="badge bg-warning">
                                                <i class="fas fa-clock"></i> Late
                                            </span>
                                            {% else %}
                                            <span class="badge bg-danger">
                                                <i class="fas fa-times"></i> Absent
                                            </span>
                                            {% endif %}
                                        </td>
                                    </tr>
                                    {% endfor %}
                                </tbody>
                            </table>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    {% endfor %}
                </div>
            </div>
            {% else %}
            <div class="card shadow-sm">
                <div class="card-body text-center py-5">
                    <i class="fas fa-clipboard fa-3x text-muted mb-3"></i>
                    <h5 class="text-muted">No Attendance Records Yet</h5>
                    <p class="text-muted mb-4">You haven't marked any attendance for this activity yet.</p>
                    <a href="{{ url_for('tutor_attendance', activity_id=activity.id) }}" class="btn btn-primary">
                        <i class="fas fa-clipboard-check me-2"></i>Mark Attendance Now
                    </a>
                </div>
            </div>
            {% endif %}
        </div>
    </div>
</div>

<style>
    .avatar-sm {
        width: 30px;
        height: 30px;
        border-radius: 50%;
        display: flex;
        align-items-center;
        justify-content: center;
        font-weight: bold;
        font-size: 14px;
    }
</style>
<p>{% endblock %}
```</p></body></html>